           About MDA Information Systems LLC
          MDA Information Systems LLC
         is a major supplier of weather information and geospatial intelligence. The firm serves a diverse client base including commercial and governmental organizations in agriculture, energy, defense, and civilian government. MDA is an industry leader in Earth observation remote sensing technology, image processing, as well as commercial weather observing and forecasting services. We also build satellite ground systems that enable users to acquire and process imagery from the most sophisticated Earth-observing satellites in the world through a direct downlink to their specific location.
